settings.title: Introducing Raizo: A luxury footwear line for women
settings.subheading: Established by a husband & wife team in 2017, RAIZO offers the finest combination of fashion, quality, and comfort in luxury footwear. RAIZO appreciates women’s passion for high heels and understands the need to make the heels as comfortable as they are stylish. Every pair is crafted with the softest leather, while artisans meticulously add soft cushions to the sole of each pair to provide relief without any added bulk. RAIZO strives to ensure women can find a pair of high heels to match their mood, occasion, and any outfit every time they get dressed!

settings.title: Year Of The Tiger: Happy Lunar New Years!
settings.text: Lunar New Year marks the end of winter and the beginning of spring! 2022 is the Year of the Tiger, the zodiac that stands for strength, ambition, and courage. We've curated a collection in celebration of the Tiger and what it stands for. We hope each piece empowers you to be bold in whatever you do!

settings.heading: Wei Beauty | China
settings.text_content: Wei was inspired to create her own beauty line on the belief that more people could benefit from this traditional way of healing illness with nature. Wei Beauty uses a treasured recipe known as the Royal Ming formula to balance Yin and Yang and remove toxic elements and to restore and rejuvenate the skin.
